OL,5,G1005 Trucking Hell
OL,6,     FThe men and women working in the
OL,7,     Fheavy recovery business are
OL,8,     Ffollowed.
OL,9,G1105 Outback Truckers
OL,10,     FOutback legend Steve Grahame is
OL,11,     Fhauling three million dollars'
OL,12,     Fworth of vital power generating
OL,13,     Fequipment to Kalumburu, an
OL,14,     Fisolated community in the far
OL,15,     FNorth West of Australia.
OL,16,G1205 Outback Truckers
OL,17,     FIt's mid-afternoon in Perth and
OL,18,     FDion's super size convoy is
OL,19,     Fpushing hard to get out of the
OL,20,     Fcity before sunset. And the fate
OL,21,     Fof Steve's trip hangs on one phone
OL,22,     Fcall to his mechanic.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
