OL,5,G1300 Outback Truckers
OL,6,     FOver the last three days, Steve
OL,7,     FGrahame has hauled 130 tonnes of
OL,8,     Ffreight a massive 2000 km, and his
OL,9,     Ftruck's taken a beating. Under the
OL,10,     Fbonnet the news isn't good.
OL,11,G1400 Outback Truckers
OL,12,     FA driver travels through an area
OL,13,     Fwhere bush fire has run wild. An
OL,14,     Fowner operator faces the busiest
OL,15,     Fweek of his career.
OL,16,G1500 Outback Truckers
OL,17,     FTurbo gambles his truck and his
OL,18,     Flife to complete an epic journey
OL,19,     Fhome. Plus, logging trucker Brett
OL,20,     Fhas a battle on his hands to
OL,21,     Fdeliver some huge machines deep
OL,22,     Finto a mountain forest.
